音韻學專題：優選論                       TOPICS IN PHONOLOGY: OPTIMALITY THEORY


  	本課程主要目標在於使學生熟悉優選論的邏輯與架構。藉由學習與討論此理論對音韻現象之應用，學生能夠學會如何將理論應用於實際的語言資料。

內容著重於熟悉優選論如何應用在世界上各種音韻及構詞現象，以期學生能夠活用。This course aims to equip students with the logic and theoretical framework behind Optimality Theory. By examining and discussing the wide and deep application of this theory to account for phonological phenomena, the students will come to know how to apply the theory to data.

The course focuses on how Optimality Theory has been applied to deal with various phonological and morphological processes in the world, so that the students will have a better command of the theory.


課程教育目標 

A 強化外國文學、文化、語言學理論與知識 To enable students to improve their knowledge and theory in the fields of foreign literatures, cultures and linguisticsB 培育外國文學及語言學領域的專業教學與學術研究人才 To cultivate talented people specializing in teaching and research in the disciplines of foreign literatures and linguisticsC 訓練學生進行研究、撰寫學術論文的能力 To enable students to develop their capabilities for research and academic writingD 培養獨立整合及創意思考的能力，發展專業且獨特研究觀點 To enable students to cultivate their capabilities for independent integration and creativie thinking and  develop their professionalism and unique research perspectives 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

B 獨立思考、思辨、反省與推己及人

C 發揮專業、擴展國際視野、跨界學習

E 熟稔各種理論基礎、收集分析文獻資料的能力

F 完成學術論文及批判性書寫的能力

G 深入閱讀並解析外國文學、語言、文化等作品與論文的能力


